	<summary>
	4/13/1994--Introduced.
Directs the Secretary of Education to make demonstration grants to local government agencies and nonprofit community-based organizations for mentor programs for at-risk youth in economically distressed communities. Sets forth requirements for such programs, priorities, applications, and evaluation. Authorizes appropriations.

